duties_responsibilities.duty: Performing fast-paced and physical warehouse work including loading, unloading, and sorting of packages of various sizes.
Working one shift a day for part time employees and two shifts for full time employees, with shift lengths varying based on package volume.
Adhering to safety procedures and regulations while working.
Receiving competitive wages beginning at $17.00 per hour for both full and part time opportunities, with overtime paid after 40 hours a week.
